    "feat": {
        "name": "Perfect Pitch",
        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "subtype": "feat",
        "text": "Your ear for harmony has enhanced your ability with musical magic. You can use Performance to Learn a Spell or Identify Magic spells and effects that are musical in nature. In addition, you gain the Pitch-Perfect Projection action.  \n  \n**Pitch-Perfect Projection** (auditory, spellshape) By using your perfect pitch, you can amplify your voice to cause magical auditory effects to reach further. If your next action this round is to Cast a Spell or use an action that creates an auditory effect with a range, increase that range by 30 feet.",
        "level": 12,
